data.description: This renovated residence situated in the sought-after Shadowridge Community is a buyer's delight. The tranquil neighborhood boasts broad streets, well-maintained sidewalks, and picturesque views. With 4 bedrooms plus a bonus room, 3 bathrooms, an updated kitchen, new luxury vinyl plank floors, and a 3-car garage, this home offers both style and functionality. The floor plan features a downstairs bedroom and full bath, ideal for guests or family members seeking single-floor living. The backyard provides a mix of sun and shade on the patio, ample green space, and a scenic view of a park for peaceful sunset evenings. Upstairs, the expansive primary bedroom with numerous windows and a stunning spa-like bathroom retreat adds to the home's appeal. Enjoy the prime location close to Carlsbad and Vista amenities, with low HOA fees and no Mello Roos. Take a short stroll to Buena Vista Park to complete the perfect living experience!
